**Summary:**
This documentation covers the Amplitude Unified SDK for Swift (beta), which is a wrapper around Analytics SDK (AmplitudeSwift), Experiment SDK, and Session Replay SDK, providing unified initialization, configuration, and identity management across all three products with automatic synchronization of user/device IDs.

